    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The observational registry study provides high-fidelity empirical RH data across the full clinical operating envelope, and Bland-Altman comparison confirms CFD predictions are within the pre-specified acceptance corridor (bias −0.031, LoA ±0.18). The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2. The credibility assessment team unanimously concludes that the CFD model is sufficiently credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
